<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">###<sp/>Full<sp/>Workflow<sp/>with<sp/>All<sp/>Features</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```bash</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>Stage<sp/>your<sp/>changes</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">git<sp/>add<sp/>.</highlight></codeline>
