<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>The<sp/>commit<sp/>is<sp/>automatically<sp/>completed<sp/>after<sp/>you<sp/>save<sp/>and<sp/>exit<sp/>the<sp/>editor</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>Troubleshooting</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">###<sp/>Common<sp/>Issues</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">1.<sp/>**&quot;No<sp/>LLM<sp/>model<sp/>or<sp/>API<sp/>token<sp/>provided&quot;**</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>Run<sp/>`penify<sp/>config<sp/>llm`<sp/>to<sp/>configure<sp/>a<sp/>local<sp/>LLM,<sp/>or</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>Run<sp/>`penify<sp/>login`<sp/>to<sp/>authenticate<sp/>with<sp/>Penify</highlight></codeline>
